Package: lmd
Depends: lmd-server, lmd-manager-cli, lmd-lliurex-data
Architecture: all
Description: LMD Metapackage
 This package contains all dependencies to prepare 
 an LTPS/LMD server.


Package: lmd-server
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, dnsmasq, ltsp-server-standalone, ltsp-server, php7.2-cli, apache2, libapache2-mod-php7.2, n4d-remote-gui-plugin, llx-netinstall ( >= 0.21), n4d-lliurex-base ( >= 0.6 ), python3, syslinux-common, llx-bootmanager (>>0.1), util-linux, python3-apt,  xpra ( >= 0.17.3-1), n4d-taskscheduler-server, n4d-taskscheduler-client
Conflicts: lliurex-ltsp, n4d-ltsp-plugins
Replaces: lliurex-ltsp, n4d-ltsp-plugins
Architecture: all
Description: LMD - LTSP Management for Dummies.
 This package gives support to Thin and Fat
 Thin Clients Management.

Package: lmd-manager-cli
