Package: lmd-lliurex-data
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, lmd-server, lliurex-preseed-common (>= 0.17)
Conflicts: lliurex-ltsp
Architecture: all
Description: LMD - LTSP links and data for LliureX.
 This package contains all cool data, links
 and templates to working with LMD in LliureX.

Package: lmd-usb-mount-disabler
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Architecture: all
Replaces: lliurex-up
Description: Disable usb mounts for thin clients.
 This Package write gconf configuration to disable automount usb devices 
 on thin clients

Package: admin-center-ltsp
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, admin-center
Architecture: all
Description: LMD - LTSP Module for admin-center.
